Thomson, J., dissenting.

Opinion filed December 2, 1925.Brown, Fox & Blumberg, for appellant; John R. Guilliams, Charles LeRoy Brown, Frank L. Kriete and Joseph D. Ryan, of counsel.Stebbins, Garey, L’Amoreaux & Hurtubise, for appellee; W. B. O’Brien and James C. Byrne, of counsel. Mr. Justice Taylor
